    {
      "id": "t33",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout16_content-left > div.margin-bottom > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "IOI Oleochemical operates within one of Asia's largest palm-based chemical producers. We convert raw materials into specialty chemicals that serve industries worldwide, backed by decades of operational excellence and technical depth.",
      "cn": "IOI Oleochemical 隶属亚洲规模最大的棕榈基化工生产商之一。我们将原材料转化为服务全球各行业的特种化学品，背后是数十年的卓越运营与深厚技术积淀。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t34",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div#w-node-c5be961c-3e1f-b35c-5c46-04386c723ad5-b8ee20cb > div.layout16_item-text-wrapper > p",
      "en": "Vertically integrated from plantation to finished product",
      "cn": "从种植园到成品的垂直整合体系"
    },
    {
      "id": "t35",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div#w-node-c5be961c-3e1f-b35c-5c46-04386c723adb-b8ee20cb > div.layout16_item-text-wrapper > p",
      "en": "Certified across quality, safety and environmental standards",
      "cn": "通过品质、安全与环境标准全方位认证"
    },
    {
      "id": "t36",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div#w-node-c5be961c-3e1f-b35c-5c46-04386c723ae1-b8ee20cb > div.layout16_item-text-wrapper > p",
      "en": "Serving personal care, home care, food, industrial and pharmaceutical sectors",
      "cn": "服务于个人护理、家居护理、食品、工业与制药等多个领域"
    },
    {
      "id": "t37",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.max-width-large > div.margin-bottom > div.text-style-tagline",
      "en": "Vision",
      "cn": "愿景"
    },
    {
      "id": "t38",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.text-align-center > div.max-width-large > h2.heading-style-h4",
      "en": "To be the trusted partner for sustainable oleochemical solutions across every sector we serve. We advance industries through innovation, reliability and responsible sourcing.",
      "cn": "成为各服务领域中值得信赖的可持续油脂化学解决方案合作伙伴。我们以创新、可靠与负责任的采购推动行业发展。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t39",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.max-width-large > div.margin-bottom > h2.heading-style-h2",
      "en": "Our core values",
      "cn": "我们的核心价值观"
    },
    {
      "id": "t40",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.text-align-center > div.max-width-large > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "We operate with clarity and purpose. Every decision reflects our commitment to quality and sustainability to the industries we serve.",
      "cn": "我们以清晰的目标驱动运营。每一项决策都体现着我们对所服务行业的品质承诺与可持续追求。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t41",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div#w-node-c5be961c-3e1f-b35c-5c46-04386c723b06-b8ee20cb > a.layout505_tab-link > h3.heading-style-h5",
