      "cn": "卓越执行"
    },
    {
      "id": "t47",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout505_tab-content-top > div.margin-bottom > h3.heading-style-h3",
      "en": "We do the right thing",
      "cn": "坚守正道"
    },
    {
      "id": "t48",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout505_tab-content > div.layout505_tab-content-top > p",
      "en": "Transparency guides our business. We keep our word and stand behind what we make.",
      "cn": "透明度是我们经营的根基。我们恪守承诺，对所制造的每一件产品负责。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t49",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout505_tab-content-top > div.margin-bottom > h3.heading-style-h3",
      "en": "We work as one",
      "cn": "齐心协力"
    },
    {
      "id": "t50",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout505_tab-content > div.layout505_tab-content-top > p",
      "en": "Our strength comes from people working together toward shared goals. We collaborate across teams and borders.",
      "cn": "我们的力量源自众人朝着共同目标携手前行。我们跨团队、跨地域协同合作。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t51",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout505_tab-content-top > div.margin-bottom > h3.heading-style-h3",
      "en": "Solve problems in better ways",
      "cn": "创新求解之道"
    },
    {
      "id": "t52",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout505_tab-content > div.layout505_tab-content-top > p",
      "en": "Our chemists and engineers embrace innovation and explore emerging technologies. We invest in research that disrupts industries and redefines what's possible.",
      "cn": "我们的化学家与工程师拥抱创新、探索前沿技术，致力于颠覆行业、重塑可能的研发投入。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t53",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout505_tab-content-top > div.margin-bottom > h3.heading-style-h3",
      "en": "We own our impact",
      "cn": "担当影响"
    },
    {
      "id": "t54",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout505_tab-content > div.layout505_tab-content-top > p",
      "en": "From plantation to product, we take ownership and put our heart into what we do.",
      "cn": "从种植园到成品，我们始终亲力亲为，倾注全心。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t55",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout505_tab-content-top > div.margin-bottom > h3.heading-style-h3",
      "en": "Getting the best value",
      "cn": "创造最佳价值"
    },
    {
      "id": "t56",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout505_tab-content > div.layout505_tab-content-top > p",
      "en": "Precision ensures optimal value for your investment.",
      "cn": "精准把控，让每一分投入都换来最优回报。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t57",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout505_tab-content-top > div.margin-bottom > h3.heading-style-h3",
      "en": "We measure and improve",
      "cn": "衡量改进"
    },
    {
      "id": "t58",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout505_tab-content > div.layout505_tab-content-top > p",
      "en": "We monitor our performance to ensure great results across all operations.",
      "cn": "我们持续监测各项运营表现，确保全面达成卓越成果。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t59",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout19_content-left > div.margin-bottom > div.text-style-tagline",
      "en": "Integrated",
      "cn": "整合体系"
    },
    {
      "id": "t60",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout19_content-left > div.margin-bottom > h2.heading-style-h2",
      "en": "One supply chain from soil to shelf",
      "cn": "从土壤到货架的完整供应链"
    },
    {
      "id": "t61",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout19_content-left > div.margin-bottom > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "IOI Oleochemical operates within IOI Corporation Berhad's vertically integrated system. We control every stage, from sustainable palm cultivation through refining, conversion, and specialty formulation. This integration means consistency, traceability and the kind of quality assurance that comes from owning the entire process.",
      "cn": "IOI Oleochemical 隶属 IOI 集团的垂直整合体系。我们掌控每一个环节——从可持续棕榈种植，到精炼、转化与特种配方。整合带来稳定性、可追溯性，以及源自全流程把控的品质保证。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t62",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "ul.layout19_list > li.layout19_item > p",
      "en": "Plantation management and sustainable sourcing",
      "cn": "种植园管理与可持续采购"
    },
    {
      "id": "t63",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "ul.layout19_list > li.layout19_item > p",
      "en": "Refining and processing of raw materials",
      "cn": "原材料精炼与加工"
    },
    {
      "id": "t64",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "ul.layout19_list > li.layout19_item > p",
      "en": "Specialty chemical conversion and formulation",
      "cn": "特种化学品转化与配方"
    },
    {
      "id": "t65",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.text-align-center > div.margin-bottom > div.text-style-tagline",
      "en": "Corporate Milestones",
      "cn": "发展历程"
    },
    {
      "id": "t66",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.text-align-center > div.margin-bottom > h2.heading-style-h2",
      "en": "Five decades of building capability",
      "cn": "五十年实力沉淀"
    },
    {
      "id": "t67",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.max-width-large > div.text-align-center > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "From our first refinery to a global network, we've grown by staying focused on what matters. Each milestone marks a commitment kept.",
      "cn": "从第一座炼厂到遍布全球的网络，我们始终专注本业、稳健前行。每一座里程碑，都是一份兑现的承诺。"
    },
